casebody.data:
K.C., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF CHILDREN & FAMILIES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-2158 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. June 5, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The petition for belated appeal is transferred to the 10th Judicial Circuit Court for Polk County for consideration as a petition for writ of habeas corpus. See In re E.H., 609 So. 2d 1289 , 1290 (Fla. 1992).

SILBERMAN, BLACK, and BADALAMENTI, JJ., Concur.
